data.description: This stunning residence boasts an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, creating a spacious and welcoming atmosphere. The recently renovated kitchen features expansive quartz countertops, 42-inch white shaker style cabinets, and a suite of stainless-steel appliances.   The master bathroom has been tastefully remodeled, now offering a zero-entry walk-in shower. The first floor is adorned with elegant tile, while the second level features beautifully engineered flooring. A bonus is the versatile room on the second floor, perfect for use as a 4th bedroom or home office. Other notable features include a new roof replaced in 2018.  Stoneybrook at Estero offers a wide array of amenities including three pools, a well-equipped gym, pickle ball courts, tennis courts, a playground, and basketball courts with all low HOA fees!  Conveniently nestled between Naples and Fort Myers, with quick access to a multitude of shopping centers, including the popular Miromar Outlet Mall, Coconut Pointe, Gulf Coast Town Center, RSW International Airport, and FGCU campus. Plus, the Gulf Coast beaches are just a short drive away.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your new home!
